lead_paragraph: Jean Segura had three hits, drove in two runs and made the top defensive play for an Arizona Diamondbacks split squad in an 8-8, nine-inning tie with the San Diego Padres on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Segura Gets 3 More Hits for D-Backs in 8-8 Tie With Padres
